query:
query GenericAnalyticsQuery {
  context {
    langUrlPrefix
    countryCode
    __typename
  }
  analytics {
    config {
      debug
      version
      ga_codes
      ga_plugins
      ga_params
      ym_codes
      city
      district
      region_id
      device_type
      user_id
      user_type
      owner
      chunk_name
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}

query productsPageQuery($ids: [Int!]!) {
  productList(ids: $ids) {
    ...ProductItemInfoFragment
    __typename
  }
}

fragment ProductItemInfoFragment on Product {
  id
  ...ProductPresenceFragment
  ...ProductItemInfoMainFragment
  __typename
}

fragment ProductPresenceFragment on Product {
  presence {
    title
    presence
    isAvailable
    isEnding
    isOrderable
    isWait
    isPresenceSure
    __typename
  }
  __typename
}

fragment ProductItemInfoMainFragment on Product {
  id
  ...ProductGalleryImageFragment
  name: nameForCatalog
  company_id
  signed_id
  groupId
  categoryId
  categoryIds
  customOrderId
  customOrderUrl
  image(width: 200, height: 200)
  imageAlt: image(width: 640, height: 640)
  buyButtonDisplayType
  productTypeKey
  urlForProductCatalog
  hasDiscount
  price
  priceFrom
  priceUSD
  priceOriginal
  priceCurrency
  priceCurrencyLocalized
  noPriceText
  discountedPrice
  discountPercent
  discountDaysLabel
  measureUnit
  sellingType
  wholesalePrices {
    price
    __typename
  }
  isService
  comparisonUrl
  isWholesale
  isAdult
  isNewYear
  company {
    id
    name
    signedId
    isChatVisible
    isContactNowAllowed
    timedHash
    regionName(branchFirst: true)
    opinionPositivePercent
    opinionTotal
    opinionTotalInRating
    companyOpinionsUrl
    __typename
  }
  report_start_chat_url
  oioCategories
  canShowPrice
  isOrderable
  __typename
}

fragment ProductGalleryImageFragment on Product {
  id
  name: nameForCatalog
  imageGallery: image(width: 700, height: 500)
  imagesGallery: images(width: 640, height: 640)
  imagesAltGallery: images(width: 700, height: 500)
  __typename
}
